verbose_text: The SPs of the Rahman and ICP1 +/+ strains resulted in a significant decrease in IL-8 production in HMC-1 cells compared with the SPs of wild-type Entamoeba, suggesting that a reduction in CP activity may result in a significant reduction of SP induced IL-8 production in HMC-1 cells.
